sentences.english: Show all articles on this topic.
sentences.chinese: 顯示所有關於這個主題的文章。

sentences.english: All eastbound trains have been cancelled due to faulty signals.
sentences.chinese: 所有向東開去的火車由於信號錯誤而均被取消。

sentences.english: All non-Nepalese students enrolled at any of Hong Kong's universities are eligible to participate in the contest.
sentences.chinese: 所有非尼泊爾裔香港註冊大學學生均可參加。

sentences.english: All these writers run to sentiment.
sentences.chinese: 所有這些作家都有傷感的傾向。

sentences.english: All of them insisted on my staying with them a few days longer.
sentences.chinese: 他們所有的人都堅持要我再跟他們多呆幾天時間。

sentences.english: Bll the boys laughed to hear the good news.
sentences.chinese: 聽見這個好動靜然後，所有的男孩都笑了。

sentences.english: None of this will actually be decided at Bali.
sentences.chinese: 所有這一切實際上都決定在巴里島。

sentences.english: All the female cats wanted to be the cat"s wife."
sentences.chinese: 所有母貓都想做他的夫人。

sentences.english: It delivers value more slowly to everyone. Invariably.
sentences.chinese: 這會讓交付價值變得更慢，對所有客戶都會變慢。

sentences.english: Entire malls will become ghost towns.
sentences.chinese: 所有的大型商場都將變得門可羅雀。

sentences.english: Hast thou not milked me as milk, and curdled me like cheese?
sentences.chinese: 所有的奶酪都來自凝結的牛奶。

sentences.english: All grocery shopping bags contain at least one stick of French bread.
sentences.chinese: 所有超市購物袋裏都裝着至少一根法式長棍麪包。

sentences.english: Some day his pictures will be worth more than all you have in your shop.
sentences.chinese: 有一天，他的畫會比你店裏所有的一切還值錢。

sentences.english: Many southerners said all of the North was responsible for the raid.
sentences.chinese: 許多南方人說，所有的北方人都應該對這次襲擊負責。

sentences.english: All patients were treated with anterior interbody fusion and internal fixation.
sentences.chinese: 所有患者爲前路植骨融合加內固定術。
